Automotive Noise, Vibration & Harshness (NVH) Materials Market Size, Share, and Forecast Analysis
The Automotive Noise, Vibration & Harshness (NVH) Materials Market has demonstrated robust growth over recent years, driven by escalating consumer expectations for comfort, stringent regulatory standards, and technological advancements in vehicle design. As of the latest market assessment, the global NVH materials market valuation stands at approximately USD 4.2 billion, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of around 6.5% over the past five years. This growth trajectory underscores the increasing emphasis on acoustic comfort and vibration mitigation in modern automotive engineering.

